# AI Video Generation Platform from Supabase Articles

Build a production-ready local application that automatically converts technical articles stored in Supabase into professional YouTube videos.

## Goal

The user should only publish an article.

Everything else must happen automatically.

Final output:

* video.mp4
* thumbnail.png
* subtitles.srt
* title.txt
* description.txt
* tags.txt
* youtube.json

---

## Tech Stack

Frontend:

* Next.js
* TailwindCSS

Backend:

* FastAPI (preferred) or Express.js

Database:

* Supabase

Local AI:

* Ollama

Video Engine:

* Remotion

Video Rendering:

* FFmpeg

Voice:

* Piper TTS

Subtitle generation:

* From narration timestamps

Upload:

* YouTube API

Package Manager:

* pnpm

Language:

* TypeScript where possible

