## Features

### 1. Supabase Integration

Connect to Supabase.

Watch for newly published articles.

Table example:

articles

id

title

slug

content

tags

published

youtube_generated

youtube_url

When:

published=true

and

youtube_generated=false

Start the pipeline automatically.

---

### 2. AI Script Generator

Using Ollama.

Input:

Markdown article.

Output:

JSON only.

Example:

{
"title": "...",
"duration": 300,
"scenes":[]
}

Each scene contains:

scene_number

title

duration

voiceover

scene_type

assets

animations

camera

code_blocks

terminal_commands

diagram

background

subtitle

No markdown.

No explanations.

Only JSON.

